text: Pazo dos Deportes Paco Paz is a multi-purpose sports arena in Ourense, Galicia, Spain. Founded in 1988, it is owned by the Deputación de Ourense. ==References== ==External links== *Official website (in Galician language) Category:Basketball venues in Spain Category:Sports venues in Galicia (Spain) Category:Sports venues completed in 1988
